        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Modern couples are looking beyond just a ring design - they want meaning, ethics, beauty and value. This shift in mindset has led to an increasing popularity of lab grown diamond jewelry. What was once a niche is now a preferred and loved choice for engagements, anniversaries, all grand milestones worth celebrating and everyday luxury. Celebrities are becoming torch bearers of a movement to inspire youngsters to choose lab grown diamond jewelry for its enhanced beauty and a better cause, while also getting a better value. Whether you are looking for rings lab created diamonds or earrings diamond, luxury is no more about the rarity of diamonds, but about how responsibly and thoughtfully it is crafted.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kKqW7n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " What Are Lab Grown Diamonds: A Quick Glimpse",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2> What Are Lab Grown Diamonds: A Quick Glimpse</h2><p>Lab grown diamonds are rxeal diamonds cultivated in laboratories using advanced technologies to create minimal environmental impact. A common misconception is that lab grown diamonds are not real diamonds, but in fact they are chemically, physically and optically the same as mined diamonds. They have the same physical and chemical structure as natural diamonds. Renowned jewelry brands provide an <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/pages/certificate?_pos=1&_psq=CER&_ss=e&_v=1.0\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IGI/SGI certification\">IGI/SGI certification</a> that ensures that these diamonds are real along with other diamond details mentioned in the certificate. If you place a natural diamond and a lab grown diamond side by side, there will be no difference to a naked eye, even if checked by a gemologist. The difference can be traced by using special equipment only. </p>",
            "custom_id": "what-are",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
