        "rich_text_PYNpgj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Value And Affordability Of Lab Grown Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Value And Affordability Of Lab Grown Diamonds</h2><p>Lab grown diamonds do not just offer enhanced beauty with precision, but also the lab grown diamond cost is much lower! With advanced technology, lab grown diamonds offer better brilliance with better value. With enlarged stones in lab grown diamond jewelry, your dream diamond ring doesn’t ask you to compromise on your budget. While their resale value, like any other diamond jewelry, is limited, their upfront cost is very low. This also gives couples a chance to upgrade to higher clarity or a bigger carat size with every milestone crossed, while also helping them choose a more intricate design and elaborate diamond setting. Fine Jewelry, with lab grown diamonds, doesn’t ask you to compromise on your travel plans or stick to just one piece - but allow you to build a luxury wardrobe with various timeless pieces for your occasion.</p>",
            "custom_id": "value",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Busting Lab Grown Diamonds Myths",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Busting Lab Grown Diamonds Myths</h2><p>There are many misconceptions about lab grown diamonds and it’s time we bust them! </p><p> 1] Lab Grown Diamonds Are Fake<br/>Truth: Lab grown diamonds are 100% real diamonds - not cubic zirconia, not crystal. Actual real diamonds! </p><p>2 ] They don’t last<br/>Truth: Let’s bust this myth with scientific facts! Lab grown diamonds, just like natural diamonds, rank 10/10 on Moh’s scale, meaning they are just as durable. With our quality lab grown diamonds, they are precisely cut with no inclusions. <br/><br/>3] They don’t have certifications <br/>Truth: Lucira lab grown diamonds are SGI and IGI certified. Our diamond jewelry is certified to ensure that our customers can trust in what we craft. SGI and IGI certification includes all details you need to verify while buying from your seller such as the carat and the cut. <br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "busting",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
